setValue against Java beans, maps, arrays, constructors, static members, method calls, and OgnlContext/MemberAccess. If tests exercise optional OGNL feature flags such as ognl.security.manager, ognl.UseJDK9PlusAccessHandler, or ognl.UseFirstMatchGetSetLookup, set and restore them within the specific test and account for OgnlRuntime static initialization.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The observed Java-run failure is consistent with a behavior change in ObjectPropertyAccessor access checks between 3.2.21 and 3.3.5, not missing setup.\",\n    \"Tests around SecurityManager, Unsafe, or deep reflection can be brittle on JDK 25 and should be scoped carefully rather than enabled globally.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_024849f707ac52a6016a4215a99f7c8197a396c207fc400ded\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1301, "output": 776, "cacheRead": 46592, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48669, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782715806113, "responseId": "resp_024849f707ac52a6016a42159ec1008197813ba08bc45204fa"}}
